---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="about-layout animate-fade">
    <div class="about-main">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="lead">Hi, I’m Senne, a 22-year-old Creative Developer and Designer based in Buggenhout. I am currently heading into my third and final year of Digital Design & Development (Devine) at Howest Kortrijk.</p>
      
      <div class="bio-block">
        <h2>Leadership & Soft Skills</h2>
        <p>Beyond code and screens, I have spent 16 years in the Chiro (youth movement), serving 4 years as a youth leader and 3 years as the group leader (groepsleider).</p>
        <p>Leading a group of over 200 kids and adolescents and managing a team of 35 co-leaders taught me skills like communication, crisis management, organization, planning, and mainly: <strong>working as a team</strong>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bio-block">
        <h2>Freelance & Collaborations</h2>
        <p>I am registered as a student-entrepreneur and am currently available for freelance projects (working remotely or on-site).</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">[ Let's connect ]</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skills-sidebar">
      <h2>Hard Skills</h2>
      
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Frontend & Creative Dev</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>HTML5 / CSS3 / JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
          <li>TypeScript</li>
          <li>React & Astro</li>
          <li>Git & GitHub</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3>Design & Motion</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>UI/UX Design (Figma)</li>
          <li>Prototyping</li>
          <li>Adobe Creative Suite (Illustrator, Photoshop)</li>
          <li>Motion Design (After Effects)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .bio-block p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .cta-wrapper {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .skills-sidebar {
    background: #fafafa;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    align-self: start;
  }

  .skills-sidebar h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category ul {
    list-style-type: none;
  }

  .skill-category li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>